OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1774624292
OL,3,CWhat are capybaras? The search
OL,4,Ccontinues for giant rodent which
OL,5,Cescaped from zoo
OL,7,FZookeepers were quickly able to locate
OL,8,Fand re-capture Tango, but Samba was
OL,9,F"more adventurous", the zoo said, and
OL,10,Fevaded capture.
OL,12,FDrone teams have been out searching
OL,13,Fand camera traps have been dotted
OL,14,Faround to try to spot her but with no
OL,15,Fluck so far.
OL,17,FVideo footage of Samba resting on a
OL,18,Fbank of the River Itchen, near
OL,19,FWinchester, was shared earlier this
OL,20,Fweek by a dog walker.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
