OL,3,CWhat are capybaras? The search
OL,4,Ccontinues for giant rodent which
OL,5,Cescaped from zoo
OL,7,FBut what are capybaras, the world's
OL,8,Fbiggest rodent species?
OL,10,FAccording to Laura Read, the Chief
OL,11,FExecutive of Marwell Wildlife,
OL,12,Fcapybaras like Samba are related to
OL,13,Fanimals such as guinea pigs, mice and
OL,14,Frats.
OL,16,FThey are native to South America and
OL,17,Fare semi-aquatic, living in and around
OL,18,Frivers, riverbanks, or waterways.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
