OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1774624292
OL,3,CWhat are capybaras? The search
OL,4,Ccontinues for giant rodent which
OL,5,Cescaped from zoo
OL,7,FWhen they feel threatened, they jump
OL,8,Finto the water and hide where they can
OL,9,Fhold their breath underwater for up to
OL,10,F10 minutes.
OL,12,FSamba will be eating a vegetarian diet
OL,13,Fin the wild like other capybaras which
OL,14,Fincludes grass, leaves and fruit.
OL,16,FMs Read described them as "gentle" and
OL,17,F"calm", explaining they don't pose a
OL,18,Frisk to anyone.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
