OL,3,CWhat are capybaras? The search
OL,4,Ccontinues for giant rodent which
OL,5,Cescaped from zoo
OL,7,FShe said they like to be social and
OL,8,Flive in big groups with other
OL,9,Fcapybaras.
OL,11,FAt nine months old, Samba is not yet
OL,12,Ffully grown and is the size of a small
OL,13,Fto medium dog.
OL,15,FWhere could Samba be?
OL,17,FMs Read thinks she could be on the
OL,18,Fwaterway between Twford and Allbrook
OL,19,Fwhich is about two and a half miles
OL,20,Ffrom the zoo which would be an "ideal
OL,21,Fhabitat".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
