OL,3,CWhat are capybaras? The search
OL,4,Ccontinues for giant rodent which
OL,5,Cescaped from zoo
OL,7,FShe said: "We are following up on as
OL,8,Fmany sightings as we feel are
OL,9,Flegitimate.
OL,11,F"We have had some sightings that are a
OL,12,Fvery, long way away, as far afield as
OL,13,FBirmingham.
OL,15,F"We are not following up on those ones
OL,16,Fbecause we know that's not possible.
OL,18,F"However if we think it's a
OL,19,Flegitimate, realistic sighting we are
OL,20,Ffollowing up on that."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
