OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1774624292
OL,3,CWhat are capybaras? The search
OL,4,Ccontinues for giant rodent which
OL,5,Cescaped from zoo
OL,7,FShe explained some of the sightings
OL,8,Fhave been Muntjac deer which are about
OL,9,Fthe same size and colour as capybaras.
OL,11,FEfforts to find her
OL,13,FAs well as drones and camera traps
OL,14,Fbeing used, the zoo said: "We have
OL,15,Fbeen reviewing our use of humane
OL,16,Ftraps. We do have some badger traps
OL,17,Favailable that we have used in the
OL,18,Fpast for vaccination programmes.
OL,20,F"We know that she really likes melon
OL,21,For any strong smelling fruit.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
