OL,3,CWhat are capybaras? The search
OL,4,Ccontinues for giant rodent which
OL,5,Cescaped from zoo
OL,7,F"So we are still debating and weighing
OL,8,Fup the operational considerations
OL,9,Fabout whether to deploy those traps.
OL,11,F"But that is another thing we can try
OL,12,Fin our resource bag of tools."
OL,14,FCoping in the wild
OL,16,FMs Read said: "We are not concerned in
OL,17,Fterms of her safety other than roads
OL,18,Fwhich we are really hoping she's
OL,19,Fstaying away from.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/11
