OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1774624292
OL,3,CWhat are capybaras? The search
OL,4,Ccontinues for giant rodent which
OL,5,Cescaped from zoo
OL,7,F"She's got food, she's got no natural
OL,8,Fpredators and if she's by the water
OL,9,Fthat's where she'll feel her safest.
OL,11,F"They are great swimmers, and they
OL,12,Falways hide in the water for safety
OL,13,Fand security in the wild.
OL,15,F"We know as long as she's not too
OL,16,Fcold, she'll be ok."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
