OL,3,CWhat are capybaras? The search
OL,4,Ccontinues for giant rodent which
OL,5,Cescaped from zoo
OL,7,FShe added: "The video we saw the other
OL,8,Fday she looked fairly relaxed and she
OL,9,Flooked fairly well in terms of body
OL,10,Fcondition so that gave us quite a lot
OL,11,Fof reassurance that she's coping
OL,12,Falright and her natural instincts have
OL,13,Fkicked in.
OL,15,F"The temperature is a little bit of a
OL,16,Fconcern because it has got a lot
OL,17,Fcolder over the last two days but
OL,18,Fshe's likely to have found somewhere
OL,19,Fto burrow into."
OL,21,FWhat if I spot Samba?
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/11
