OL,3,CWhat are capybaras? The search
OL,4,Ccontinues for giant rodent which
OL,5,Cescaped from zoo
OL,7,FAnybody who sees Samba is being asked
OL,8,Fto take a photo or video of her and
OL,9,Fcall Marwell as soon as possible with
OL,10,Fa precise location.
OL,12,FPeople are being asked not to approach
OL,13,Fher so she doesn't get spooked and run
OL,14,Faway.
